{"tid":1997231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"行動告急， dsc選民登記街站行動， 人手嚴重不足","createTime":"2020-05-01T13:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T07:39:55.000Z","uid":353200,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd5a6648cc0aefcc3c857ce5512ab14b1f45dc4","tid":1997231,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"目前只有大約近200名手足參與, 我哋仲有一日可以行動， 多一票就係多,18區dse選民登記行動， 我哋呢幾日都係出面不斷咁派表， 不斷開post都冇人推， 就算你哋唔出嚟幫手都好， 可唔可以幫我哋推一推post， 至少畀想幫手嘅人趁而家加入我地,<br />\nTg group<br />\n<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA&amp;d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&amp;h=daa23394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ft.me%252Fjoinchat%252FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA%26d%3DWEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%252BS4RyAur%252Bbp9MVyOkMM5%252FMxDY%253D%26h%3Ddaa23394&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c2e75288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMi0F7hncuyROQQCA2RlaIA&amp;d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&amp;h=daa23394</a><br />\n<br />\n以下ig整合咗數學考試場地, 大家可以去返自己區度派選民登記表。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_mq3gygOPR/?igshid=f9vwvak1f4bt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_mq3gygOPR%2F%3Figshid%3Df9vwvak1f4bt&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=1f50dbf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_mq3gygOPR%2F%3Figshid%3Df9vwvak1f4bt&h=5af7a2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B_mq3gygOPR/?igshid=f9vwvak1f4bt</a><br />\n數學Dse<br />\n2/5（星期六） 8:30 - 10:45 數學 必修部分 （一）<br />\n2/5 11:30 - 12:45 數學 必修部分 （二）<br />\n<br />\n建議大家自行<br />\n印有QRcode單張 +派選民登記表格<br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=68b2aa83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民<br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=0b51ef71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=1e5fddf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=046312d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位等考生考完之後 先派選民登記表， 費事打亂佢哋嘅節奏<br />\n因為最後一日希望大家盡量畀qr code佢哋整<br />\n到場手足記得如果畀表佢哋填， 叫佢哋填完盡快交返畀我哋或者交俾區議員， 最後一日要即日送去九龍灣"},{"pid":"c4dda995c8203cc8f789e2e9afbfad42fbdc0dfe","tid":1997231,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7a144f47a47d16ac5b12fd4f4598c152ff702a","tid":1997231,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"458558f220c99a08e07ec78a2952b690250175e7","tid":1997231,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":